About 4MLinux.
4MLinux is a mini Linux distro focusing on the following &quot;4M&quot;:
 - Maintenance (system rescue Live CD),
 - Multimedia (e.g., playing video DVDs),
 - Miniserver (using the inetd daemon),
 - Mystery (console games). &lt;a href=&quot;
