2011-11-04

4MLinux-3.0-allinone-edition released.

All 4MLinux applications have been compiled under Slackware 13.37 (x86/32-bit/SMP):
 - kernel 2.6.39.2,
 - glibc 2.13,
 - gcc 4.5.2.

Have a nice Linux !
